post.title: Decode pictures
post.body:
```python
#!/usr/bin/env python
# from urllib.request import urlopen
from PIL import Image # pip install pillow
from io import BytesIO
import zlib

data = None
# with urlopen('https://i.imgur.com/JOkp9R2.png') as fd:
with open("1.png", "rb") as fd:
    data = fd.read()
print(zlib.decompress(Image.open(BytesIO(data)).tobytes(), 16+zlib.MAX_WBITS))
```
